desc:
Sudoku Creator

A smooth and powerful plugin for Supernote devices, designed to generate instant Sudoku puzzles and insert them directly into your notes as PNG images.

Powered by Wolfsolver, website: https://github.com/wolfsolver/supernote-sudoku-plugin 
Thanks to: https://sudoku-api.vercel.app/ for Sudoku API
name: sudoku_creator
author: Wolfsolver
